title: Kelly Clarkson - All I Ever Wanted 2009 (DRB123 - HIGH QUALITY)
description:
American Idol Kelly Clarkson returns with her fourth studio album, All I Ever Wanted. Seamlessly combining pop-rock riots with bright and blistering ballads, this perfectly produced pop album showcases the multiple Grammy Award winning singer-songwriter's powerful and distinctive voice with a shattering collection of sensational smash hits.
